  "text": "Predictors of maternal diagnosis of thyroid dysfunction during pregnancy and the risk of preterm birth, SGA and LGA in children born to mothers with a diagnosis of hyper-or hypothyroidism were studied in univariate and multivariate logistic regression models. Also, birth weight and length of the child and ponderal index [birth weight (kg) divided by the cube of birth length (m 3 )] [CITATION_1] were examined in linear regression models with and without adjustment for gestational age at delivery.",
